name: LUCIFER - RUCKSACK
description:
LUCIFER - RUCKSACK

TAMZIN LILLYWHITE FOR P&CO


The "LUCIFER" rucksack takes a twist on the original roll top bag with a totally reinvented base - The all black bag is sleek and has everything you could ever want from a city rucksack.

These unique pieces were designed by Tamzin Lillywhite for P&CO and hand crafted in her London Studio. We spent months collaborating with Tamzin, working our way through countless designs, until we came up with what we all think is the perfect Life | Style | Elegance inspired bag.

All Lucifer rucksacks were hand made in London.

name: Mr. Timms' replica book
description:
This book is a replica of a book that we have used since day one. Since we both sat down in a coffee shop near Christmas and started collating ideas for P&Co. This has been and still is the ideas book. The brand's history to date is doodled on the front page and the ideas are scrawled within it. Perfect bound notepad with a natural cover made from 100% recycled cardboard and approximately 75 sheets of 80gsm 100% recycled plain white paper.
Screen printed replica front design with the P&Co England logo on the reverse.
Manufactured in the UK.
BUY 2 FOR £14 | Just use code "MrTimms" as a discount code when checking out.
